{"id":1693,"date":"2021-10-20T12:09:19","date_gmt":"2021-10-20T19:09:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/?page_id=1693"},"modified":"2022-05-20T11:53:27","modified_gmt":"2022-05-20T17:53:27","slug":"emergency-restoration","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/capabilities\/emergency-restoration\/","title":{"rendered":"Emergency Restoration"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim-30 has-background-dim is-style-hero-inside\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1721\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-24-2.jpg\" style=\"object-position:65% 39%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"65% 39%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-24-2.jpg 1800w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-24-2-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-24-2-1600x960.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-24-2-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-24-2-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Emergency Restoration<sub>Here for you when you need us most<\/sub><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"#learn-more\">Learn More <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-316\" style=\"width: NaNpx;\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/arrow-down.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section has-myrgroup-gray-dark-color has-white-background-color has-text-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim is-style-left-image-content\" id=\"learn-more\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1152\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1722\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-1-Ice-Storm-2.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-1-Ice-Storm-2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-1-Ice-Storm-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-1-Ice-Storm-2-1600x900.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-1-Ice-Storm-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-1-Ice-Storm-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"is-style-has-underline wp-block-heading\">Always answering the call, no matter the hour<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When ice storms, windstorms, hurricanes, tornadoes, lightning, and earthquakes strike, we dispatch our crews to step in and restore power to our communities, local and far. Our network of companies is equipped with the personnel and equipment resources required to respond quickly and efficiently to these and other emergency events. Through our 24-hour availability, we rapidly mobilize line and safety crews to respond to those who need it. Partnering with our clients and communities, we can provide electrical services for emergency treatment facilities such as hospitals and readily available emergency mobile units.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim is-style-right-image-content\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1723\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-15-2.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-15-2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-15-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-15-2-1600x1066.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-15-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-Wichita-KS-Storm-SECO-15-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"is-style-has-underline has-black-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\">Critical responders in times of critical need<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When disaster strikes, our teams stand ready to restore power under challenging circumstances. Across the U.S., our crews have responded to some of the most devastating natural disasters. As critical responders, we know how important it is to restore power as quickly and safely as possible. Our emergency restoration crews have rebuilt hundreds of miles of distribution and transmission lines ranging from 4kV to 765kV, damaged by storms. Our powerline response teams provide everything from repairing damaged substations to clearing trees to ensure safe access to the area.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group mb-md-5\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-co